title: 'London Thumakda' singer Labh Janjua found dead at Mumbai residence
text:
Singer Labh Janjua, famous for chartbusters like 'London Thumakda' and 'Jee Karda', was found dead at his home on Thursday morning in Mumbai police said.
The Punjabi singer died at his residence in suburban Bangur Nagar, Goregaon, Additional Commissioner of Police (north region) Fatehsingh Patil said. Asked if it was a natural ... Â»
